title: [Vornavis Caravansary, Tent Lane]
description: On the north side of the path stands a wagon bearing the sword-and-anvil symbol of the weaponcrafters' guild and the grey cuirass on a blue circle symbol of the armorers' guild side-by-side.  Just to the west the path forks in front of a plank-sided tent and continues to the southwest and the northwest.
